title: Code Masters
description: October 22, 2020 - Code Masters was an online contest that tested the participants’ understanding of their lessons in IT111/L: Concepts in Object Oriented Programming Lecture/Laboratory and CS102-1/L: Data Structures and Algorithms Analysis Lecture/Laboratory courses. It was executed using Kahoot! and it served as a review for their upcoming final exams.
summary: Code Masters was an online contest that tested the participants’ understanding of their lessons in IT111/L and CS102-1/L courses.
